gen_ai.request.messages.content: I'm in a game world. What should I do first?

system_state_after.gen_ai.response.content: First, take a moment to familiarize yourself with your surroundings and any objectives or quests you may have. Explore the area, interact with characters, and gather resources. It's also a good idea to check your inventory and abilities to see what tools and skills you have at your disposal. If you have a specific goal or mission, focus on completing that first. And most importantly, have fun and enjoy the adventure!
